,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4de7734cd1ef7342ea63852d4b7aa61a6deaeea0","tid":1673690,"uid":331544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T20:02:14.000Z","msg":"金秋貢禹彈冠<br />\n煲底琅琊相伴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T20:15:03.000Z","msg":"老莊刚写的六言古诗，连登仔、有懂有不懂，没关系；不会因为您不懂、抹杀您的付出，若您懂、一片冰心月明中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T20:17:19.000Z","msg":"剛又忘記轉成香港字了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b507c25cedb78f2ce80c4fb345d68e14b81fd8","tid":1673690,"uid":331544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T20:34:45.000Z","msg":"說實在的，我對連登仔、敬佩，付出並且堅持；同時，我對連登仔的國文(英文我不懂、不敢評說)、卻汗顏。手足們看到我這樣說、第一感覺肯定不舒服、我理解，對比前線，老莊這個老不死、連冷氣軍師都算不上、我也認同。但時代革命如果成功，恐怕會將前線、冷氣軍師、老莊灰類、和理非都記功"},{"pid":"e6679f61e16d7cd06671ad2b3551cf3ac311957e","tid":1673690,"uid":331544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ce93bb2611b68f9cc83ebebf212bc1dead10599","tid":1673690,"uid":331544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75661d5423c7ec402d976f40db97edb952c7a888","tid":1673690,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T20:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guewjRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FguewjRY.jpg&h=ac95176a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T20:06:11.000Z","msg":"相輔相成，相得益彰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T21:04:17.000Z","msg":"革命不分彼此，時代進步中。若革命成功了，在革命隊伍中、卻找不到文人，也不算笑話。所以說：同構、尊重，別不合脾胃就叼。再次鄭重提醒：可以叼他本人、出來混就有預，但不要涉及其家人、這真的是出來混、幾乎所有人的底線。相濡以沫、不如相忘於江湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa76c728811e8bbaf69bedecd3a78d2332cf8ec","tid":1673690,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T23:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatorleahy